        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This one was tough for me to weigh in on. See, I'm a project car person, nothing goes unmodified in my house, so I start planning with every car I see. It got about an hour in before I had to cut myself off. Of the 93 pages of under $20K inventory on Motorious, I admittedly only got through about 7 in that hour, but I have a plan for each car on those first seven pages! ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "What I did land on (the first round, and we'll get to that), was a clean ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "1997 BMW M3 E36",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
