        "height": 1283
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "But if I could buy a $20K and the money I put into it didn't matter, we're playing a new game, and I could tell by this point that my team was already getting exhausted that I've started to break the rules. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
